511
00:25:31,596 --> 00:25:32,729
Great!

512
00:25:32,797 --> 00:25:35,566
[crew chatter]

513
00:25:35,633 --> 00:25:37,367
Print first and last.

514
00:25:37,435 --> 00:25:39,269
Okay!
[grunt]

515
00:25:39,336 --> 00:25:40,604
