for films, Davide.

1365
01:08:31,072 --> 01:08:33,574
It's a beauty.

1366
01:08:33,642 --> 01:08:35,676
It's one of
Scippione's best.

1367
01:08:35,743 --> 01:08:37,778
How much will you
give me for it?

1368
01:08:38,846 --> 01:08:40,614
No, you will not believe it,

1369
01:08:40,682 --> 01:08:42,916
