Don't you think?

1406
01:10:23,585 --> 01:10:24,618
Mmm.

1407
01:10:25,687 --> 01:10:27,188
Kristina should be happy.

1408
01:10:27,255 --> 01:10:29,590
Mmm, she is magnificent.

1409
01:10:30,658 --> 01:10:32,226
