1410
01:10:32,293 --> 01:10:35,062
and she told me
not to worry.

1411
01:10:35,130 --> 01:10:36,363
[grunts]

1412
01:10:38,800 --> 01:10:41,836
Excuse me, I have
to interrupt you.

1413
01:10:41,903 --> 01:10:43,637
But the Princess wishes

1414
01:10:43,705 --> 01:10:45,639
